Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) applied to source code summarization. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also likely as the paper discusses the benefits of code summarization for software maintenance and retrieval. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a deep reinforcement learning framework for code summarization. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper uses a machine learning approach to solve a natural language processing task. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with source code and its structure.
